{"tid":242683,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"香港話=廣東話+英文+潮語","createTime":"2017-05-14T06:03:23.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-14T06:26:55.000Z","uid":84733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8ced4c48b50cd936e4b0957a54417d527d2aeb5c","tid":242683,"uid":84733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T06:03:23.000Z","msg":"見到有post鬧香港人成日夾英文字<br />\n話咩香港人講返廣東話啦<br />\n真係睇唔過眼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n香港官方語言係中同英<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n另外香港廣東話之所以同其他廣東話唔同<br />\n係因為我地會夾英文詞語 例如我地會講做project  而唔係小組報告 仲有我地會有好多潮語 係廣州人未必識<br />\n<br />\n當然有好多人夾英文係好刻意好難聽 例如 我地burst into laughters咁 就一定係柒<br />\n所以 只要聽落順耳 夾少少係完全無問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbaab2d4d101c85aa4f39687263ca339898b81ab","tid":242683,"uid":84733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T06:13:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"adb43602c95a143efa07219d7ac103e20e7212b6","tid":242683,"uid":84055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T06:17:05.000Z","msg":"同意樓豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"200d817cf399fb68a78bcf673582b61d6ed0b841","tid":242683,"uid":84733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T06:26:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同意樓豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}